      "text": "//span[contains(text(),\"Mon\")] the contains method search for partial texts or classses or id\n//section[]/child:: tagname of child / child :: tagname--> To move hierarchically in dom-->top down traverse\n//parent tag[]/descendent:: any child you want\n//to move bottom up we use parent :: / OR ../ OR ancestor for indirect parent\n//to locate siblings we use preceding-sibling and following-sibling\n//to lacote svg tags//*[name()='path' and @class='dWptfd']\n\n",
